text = "[b]2 (Any Suit):[/b] The next player must draw 2 cards. If they have a 2, they can play it instead, making the following player draw 4 cards. This chain can continue until a player without a 2 has to draw all accumulated cards.

[b]7 (Any Suit):[/b] Skips the next player's turn.

[b]8 (Any Suit):[/b] Reverses the direction of play. In 2-player games, this works like the 7 (skip/play again).

[b]Ace (Any Suit):[/b] Can be played on any card. The player who plays it chooses which suit the next player must match.

[b]Jack (Any Suit):[/b] Allows the player to play another card immediately.

[b]King of Hearts:[/b] The next player must draw 5 cards.

[b]5 of Hearts:[/b] Cancels out the effect of the King of Hearts if played immediately after.

[b]2 of Hearts:[/b] When played after a King of Hearts, changes the penalty from 5 to 7 cards."
fit_content = true
autowrap_mode = 2

